# Attack 03 – Registry Run Key Persistence

## Objective

Simulate persistence by adding a Registry Run key.

## Attack

Added a Registry Run key using the Windows Registry.

## Detection

- Wazuh Rule: 92302
- Alert: Registry entry to be executed on next logon modified

## MITRE ATT&CK

- T1547.001 – Registry Run Keys / Startup Folder

## Investigation

Reviewed registry modification events and confirmed the persistence mechanism.

## Outcome

Persistence activity was successfully detected by Wazuh
